				.hero-card_image.hero-card_item.hero-card_image--stretch
					img(src="images/participation-picture.jpg").mx-auto.d-block.shadow-lg
			.hero-card.align-items-center.my-4.my-md-n5
				.hero-card_text.hero-card_item.px-md-5.py-3
					p.p-l Create, manage and get quick solutions across your project activities. Use the tools of recruitment and integration for your and third - open sources.
					p.p-l Flexible collaboration setting and tooling.
					p.p-l Allows you to integrate workflows at different levels.
				.hero-card_image.hero-card_item.hero-card_image--stretch
					img(src="images/participation-picture-03.jpg").mx-auto.d-block.shadow-lg
			.hero-card.align-items-center.flex-sm-row-reverse.my-4.mt-md-n5
				.hero-card_text.hero-card_item.px-md-5.py-3
					p.p-l Moderation and success.
					p.p-l Create, manage and get quick solutions across your project activities. Use the tools of recruitment and integration for your and third- open sources.
				.hero-card_image.hero-card_item.hero-card_image--stretch
					img(src="images/participation-picture-02.png").mx-auto.d-block
			.hero-card.align-items-center.my-4.mt-md-n5
				.hero-card_text.hero-card_item.px-md-5.py-3
					p.p-l Reporting and networking. Effectively determine the impact  vof your scientifically and research network activities through ConAx Tool.
				.hero-card_image.hero-card_item.hero-card_image--stretch
					img(src="images/participation-picture-04.png").mx-auto.d-block
